sectionDeptRestriction: Restricted to students in the Natural Res & Env Sci department.
sectionText: All seats in NRES 420 for Spring 2016 will be restricted to NRES majors only until November 14th, when any remaining seats will be made available to students in other majors. If all seats are full, complete the form at http://go.illinois.edu/NRESwaitinglist to be added to the waiting list.
